{"title":"月亮颂","authors":["计小为"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":12,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计小为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥洒着皎洁的光带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞动着洁白的衣裙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比窈窕的少女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在如雪的云层里徘徊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一束束的光波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荡漾在辽阔的大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莽莽的原野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩瀚的湖海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有太阳辉煌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有灯光明亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却比一切的光波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要温柔、迷人、飘香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八月中秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银河水涨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩渺宇宙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升起一轮晶莹的月亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多美的夜晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一连串的想象："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫦娥、玉兔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桂树、吴刚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么神奇的幻想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨开慧、柳直荀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士、忠魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么深情的歌唱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而，月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她只知不停地运行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完全不理会人们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不懂得人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的爱慕、思恋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢喜、悲伤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对宇宙飞船来访，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不表示欢畅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她满载着人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最奇妙、最深沉、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最美好的感情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运动、旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将那起伏的思潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带到遥远的天堂。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}